  "description": "Schedules a callback roughly every gen 2 GC (you may see a Gen 0 an Gen 1 but only once)\n(We can fix this by capturing the Gen 2 count at startup and testing, but I mostly don't care)",
  "title": "Class Gen2GcCallback",
  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback' data-commentId='T:Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback' id='Alis_Core_Ecs_Redifinition_Gen2GcCallback'>Class Gen2GcCallback    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Ecs/src/Redifinition/Gen2GcCallback.cs#L40'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h1>\r\n <div class=\"facts text-secondary\">\r\n<dl><dt>Namespace</dt><dd><a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.html'>Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition</a></dd></dl><dl><dt>Assembly</dt><dd>Alis.dll</dd></dl>\r\n</div><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Schedules a callback roughly every gen 2 GC (you may see a Gen 0 an Gen 1 but only once)\n(We can fix this by capturing the Gen 2 count at startup and testing, but I mostly don't care)</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public sealed class Gen2GcCallback : CriticalFinalizerObject</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Inheritance</h4><dl class=\"typelist inheritance\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object'>object</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.runtime.constrainedexecution.criticalfinalizerobject'>CriticalFinalizerObject</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback.html'>Gen2GcCallback</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h4 class='section'>Inherited Members</h4><dl class=\"typelist\"><dd>\r\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object)'>object.Equals(object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object-system-object)'>object.Equals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gethashcode'>object.GetHashCode()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gettype'>object.GetType()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.referenceequals'>object.ReferenceEquals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.tostring'>object.ToString()</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Constructors</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback.#cctor' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback.#cctor' id='Alis_Core_Ecs_Redifinition_Gen2GcCallback__cctor'>Gen2GcCallback()    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Ecs/src/Redifinition/Gen2GcCallback.cs#L65'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Initializes a new instance of the <xref href=\"Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> class</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>private static Gen2GcCallback()</code></pre><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback.#ctor(System.Func{System.Boolean})' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback.#ctor(System.Func{System.Boolean})' id='Alis_Core_Ecs_Redifinition_Gen2GcCallback__ctor_System_Func_System_Boolean__'>Gen2GcCallback(Func&lt;bool&gt;)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Ecs/src/Redifinition/Gen2GcCallback.cs#L78'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Initializes a new instance of the <xref href=\"Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> class</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>private Gen2GcCallback(Func&lt;bool&gt; callback)</code>