api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The target obj</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Fields</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback.Gen2CollectionOccured' data-commentId='F:Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback.Gen2CollectionOccured' id='Alis_Core_Ecs_Redifinition_Gen2GcCallback_Gen2CollectionOccured'>Gen2CollectionOccured    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Ecs/src/Redifinition/Gen2GcCallback.cs#L45'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The gen collection occured</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public static Action Gen2CollectionOccured</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Field Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.action'>Action</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback._callback0' data-commentId='F:Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback._callback0' id='Alis_Core_Ecs_Redifinition_Gen2GcCallback__callback0'>_callback0    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Ecs/src/Redifinition/Gen2GcCallback.cs#L50'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The callback</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>private readonly Func&lt;bool&gt; _callback0</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Field Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.func-1'>Func</a>&lt;<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.boolean'>bool</a>&gt;  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback._callback1' data-commentId='F:Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback._callback1' id='Alis_Core_Ecs_Redifinition_Gen2GcCallback__callback1'>_callback1    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Ecs/src/Redifinition/Gen2GcCallback.cs#L55'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The callback</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>private readonly Func&lt;object, bool&gt; _callback1</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Field Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.func-2'>Func</a>&lt;<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object'>object</a>, <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.boolean'>bool</a>&gt;  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback._weakTargetObj' data-commentId='F:Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback._weakTargetObj' id='Alis_Core_Ecs_Redifinition_Gen2GcCallback__weakTargetObj'>_weakTargetObj    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Ecs/src/Redifinition/Gen2GcCallback.cs#L60'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The weak target obj</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>private GCHandle _weakTargetObj</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Field Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.runtime.interopservices.gchandle'>GCHandle</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Methods</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback.Finalize' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback.Finalize' id='Alis_Core_Ecs_Redifinition_Gen2GcCallback_Finalize'>~Gen2GcCallback()    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Ecs/src/Redifinition/Gen2GcCallback.cs#L115'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <pre><code class='lang-csharp'>protected ~Gen2GcCallback()</code></pre><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback.Register(System.Func{System.Boolean})' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback.Register(System.Func{System.Boolean})' id='Alis_Core_Ecs_Redifinition_Gen2GcCallback_Register_System_Func_System_Boolean__'>Register(Func&lt;bool&gt;)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Ecs/src/Redifinition/Gen2GcCallback.cs#L95'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Schedule 'callback' to be called in the next GC.  If the callback returns true it is\nrescheduled for the next Gen 2 GC.  Otherwise the callbacks stop.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public static void Register(Func&lt;bool&gt; callback)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>callback</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.func-1'>Func</a>&lt;<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.boolean'>bool</a>&gt;  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback.Register(System.Func{System.Object,System.Boolean},System.Object)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback.Register(System.Func{System.Object,System.Boolean},System.Object)' id='Alis_Core_Ecs_Redifinition_Gen2GcCallback_Register_System_Func_System_Object_System_Boolean__System_Object_'>Register(Func&lt;object, bool&gt;, object)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Ecs/src/Redifinition/Gen2GcCallback.cs#L107'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Redifinition.Gen2GcCallback.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Schedule 'callback' to be called in the next GC.  If the callback returns true it is\nrescheduled for the next Gen 2 GC.  Otherwise the callbacks stop.\nNOTE: This callback will be kept alive until either the callback function returns false,\nor the target object dies.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public static void Register(Func&lt;object, bool&gt; callback, object targetObj)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>callback</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.func-2'>Func</a>&lt;<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object'>object</a>, <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.boolean'>bool</a>&gt;  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>targetObj</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object'>object</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl>",
